nodes.text: The Empire Strikes Back was the sixth expansion card pack made for the Star Wars Trading Card Game produced by Wizards of the Coast, and based on Star Wars: Episode V The Empire Strikes Back. The game was introduced on November 17, 2003. The expansion symbol was that of the Empire.

Expansion contains 210 cards including 72 rare, 69 uncommon and 69 common cards. The Empire Strikes Back was the second expansion pack after Attack of the Clones which was sold in starting sets (60 cards, playmat, rulebook and dices)
